{"tid":1653494,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"【iPhone用家注意】Safari傳用戶瀏覽資料到騰訊","createTime":"2019-10-14T05:57:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T20:32:40.000Z","uid":141060,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"ab7f05ef3c1c82d7f65327af57f18f0bd075d559","tid":1653494,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T05:57:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20191014/60151985\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191014%2F60151985&d=JMO6Z0a0EEbNsRtkVA0DAiK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=376d101d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191014%2F60151985&h=6e0152c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20191014/60151985</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2WVh91v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2WVh91v.jpg&h=953d680d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在iOS 13內Safari瀏覽器的私隱政策中，表明會將資料傳送到「騰訊安全瀏覽」。(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\niPhone用戶使用內置的Safari瀏覽器時，資料可能會被送中？著名科技網站Engadget報道，在iOS 13的Safari的瀏覽器中提供的「詐騙網站警告」功能內，除原來會將用戶瀏覽的網址及IP地址，傳到「Google安全瀏覽」驗證外，還新增了「騰訊安全瀏覽」，這引發網民的不安，目前仍未知道驣訊取得甚麼資料，最簡單的解決辦法就是關掉這個功能，或使用其他的瀏覽器，例如Google Chrome。<br />\n<br />\n報道指出，Safari一直透過將資料傳到「Google安全瀏覽」，以驗證用戶瀏覽的網站是否安全，不過，有用戶更新到iOS 13後，發現Safari將資料同時傳到「騰訊安全瀏覽」，報道指，目前仍未知道Safari將多少資料傳到騰訊，同時騰訊會否收集中國以外的瀏覽資料。<br />\n事件引發很多網民憂慮，特別是騰訊多次被指協助中國政府，收集資料以監控網民。美國約翰霍普金斯大學（Johns Hopkins University）教授Matthew Green之前亦表示，有木馬程式理論上可以利用Google安全瀏覽的資料，查出那個用戶要求瀏覽某一個網址，如果騰訊的運作與Google類似，一旦中國政府施壓，利用這方法可以查出個別網民的身份。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，目前未有具體方法安全地防止資料送中，只能將「詐騙網站警告」功能暫時關閉，但用戶可能要面對誤訪有問題的網站。<br />\n早前美國蘋果被指受到中方壓力，移除可以實時追蹤警察位置的應用程式HKmap.live，同時在更新系統後，香港、澳門的iPhone移除「青天白日滿地紅旗」的emoji。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />越黎越柒"},{"pid":"7dd4712c0562941c2c1e72ff6be8f7b6bb8b6a3f","tid":1653494,"uid":144942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T06:08:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36be12c9e32bf09f0e73eace94d8c3eec9703949","tid":1653494,"uid":236728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T06:12:57.000Z","msg":"有冇推介用邊款app取代？"},{"pid":"9aeafbbd5fc62e23f9cbd08bfc31fcb017a8afb1","tid":1653494,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T06:13:06.000Z","msg":"今次嘅重點，係要知道爛果是咪中國account 以外嘅機，都送資料比騰訊，係幾話，正！等比全世界屌爆基曲屎忽！<br />\n侵犯國際用家私隱黎送中，真係與文明世界為敵"},{"pid":"16cc1ee316bb06ef206a23226b67b219b218dc22","tid":1653494,"uid":255744,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T06:14:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a58cbc315e3aa9c076bcc6ab15a3017c7f901b3","tid":1653494,"uid":24211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"36be12c9e32bf09f0e73eace94d8c3eec9703949","tid":1653494,"uid":236728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T06:12:57.000Z","msg":"有冇推介用邊款app取代？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T06:46:49.000Z","msg":"Google Chrome"},{"pid":"a917a9f826140351def698352a0f4d08b7a00301","tid":1653494,"uid":83518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T06:51:28.000Z","msg":"轉用chrome"},{"pid":"2c17833f27472a64d6f40f84c5f816c9454b5f73","tid":1653494,"uid":294474,"like":0,"dislike":